{"tid":337402,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會出年會retake dse econ?暑期dse econ 特訓班.","createTime":"2017-07-27T09:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T08:00:30.000Z","uid":29740,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a8af9171c96bcfe709843a9ca82181913e3293","tid":337402,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"依個班係專比DSE ECON retakers<br />\n課程總共12小時<br />\n如果你考得唔好今年,未必係你唔識,而係你答唔到考評局想你答既野,又或者係有d細節位你唔係好識<br />\n依個課程主要係教授點樣考好dse econ<br />\n我會主要用pp黎做教材,以實戰經驗考授大家點考好個試<br />\n當然,大家都配合我要大家做既野,包括功課<br />\n同埋報得既同學一定要有心考好個試,無心考既野話唔好報<br />\n課程將會由8月底開始,2個星期內完成<br />\n課程將會由小組型式8-15個人,我會出去book班房<br />\n課程費用:$300元<br />\n<br />\n利申: hk alevel econ A, 大學讀ECON first hon<br />\n不是香港讀大學<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既話可以telegram我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/F8OMjgtnIlwcyXRTFXEhcQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FF8OMjgtnIlwcyXRTFXEhcQ&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=69b4fb49\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/F8OMjgtnIlwcyXRTFXEhcQ</a>"},{"pid":"f2a7ffe070fceae4f28abcfbc10d36c661f24d67","tid":337402,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278b0b798b1574b0e9af2d6488b439668a216e44","tid":337402,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed84e61b4364617f886954dac4ec906924c0888","tid":337402,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實唔明點解咁多負評<br />\n淨係出去book埸地12個鐘都成2000蚊"},{"pid":"36bf39420003372fc3f4becec0a3b6ba3358fa81","tid":337402,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike"